DESCRIPTION: | Arena Wien - Gelände | 𝗥𝗘𝗚𝗚𝗔𝗘 𝗶𝗻𝗻𝗮 𝗔𝗥𝗘𝗡𝗔 is back with a musical blast and original soundsystem vibes!  Come along and enjoy a laid-back Saturday afternoon and a hot summer night outdoors at one of Vienna's most legendary venues. Good people\, good vibes and a splendid selection of root.dub.reggae provided by:  𝗛𝗜𝗚𝗛 𝗡𝗢𝗢𝗡 𝗥𝗢𝗖𝗞𝗘𝗥𝗦 𝗦𝗢𝗨𝗡𝗗𝗦𝗬𝗦𝗧𝗘𝗠 - your #1 rootsdisco (with full sound) 𝗣𝗨𝗣𝗣𝗔 𝗥𝗔𝗬𝗡𝗔 - outta Treasure Isle Soundand 𝗙𝗜𝗦𝗛𝗘𝗥𝗠𝗔𝗡 𝗦𝗢𝗨𝗡𝗗 - the one man army!*** OPEN-AIR  *** KIDS-AREA  *** ADMISSION FREE - donations appreciated *** FOOD-CORNER hosted by 'Praterwirt' *** AFTER-PARTY at Arena Beisl with Fisherman Sound celebrating his birthday!
